item.title: Need help portfowarding -.-
item.dc:creator: @RsPsMechanic RsPsMechanic
item.description:
@RsPsMechanic wrote:

Tutorial:

I have Windstream too, and I’ll go ahead and tell you that you cannot portforward properly by just using a router. There are some security issues in the Firewall of the modem Windstream provided you. I have a built in router on my modem, so I’m not sure if any further advice I could give you would actually help or not.

Thanks man
